8.31.24  5:12 pm   why do you give such vague answers and are so vague? do you do it on purpose? or is your thought process that abstract?

      in this case, it would be to compensate for all the other times when i've answered in way way way too much specific detail

8.31.24  5:04 pm   How to be less sad?

      no one knows how to do this. even after you do it, you won't know how you did it

8.31.24  4:56 pm   Some people say there will never be anything radically and universally new in the creative space. Only smaller and smaller  fragments of personalised ideas due to everyone being constantly interconnected. Thoughts. 

      that reminds me of people thinking the highest roller coaster in the world wouldn't be able to go down, because it's so high

8.31.24  4:56 pm   what's it like being awesome sauce?

      i could imagine this scenario: let's say there is a job position where the person is supposed to be awesome sauce. i could imagine potentially an awesome sauce person being paranoid that they won't get hired for the awesome sauce job. nevermind, i'm thinking of something else

8.31.24  4:39 pm   i hate writing about music because if i could sufficiently capture what music expresses in writing i wouldn't need the music 

      of course

8.31.24  4:15 pm   Do you ever have trouble writing lyrics, and if so what do you do to get yourself writing again?

      'writing lyrics' as you say, doesn't remind me of anything i do in the songwriting process. songs are usually full of words/music. whenever i hear someone talk about a 'lyric', they're usually taking words from a song without the song. my whole reason for doing songs is for cases where that doesn't work

8.31.24  4:04 pm   I feel fear inside me, all the time. Most often, it's the strongest emotion I'm feeling. But I try to keep my actions based on my 2nd most felt emotion. Do you think that's unfair to the first place emotion?

      no

8.31.24  4:00 pm   Have you ever considered domesticating a dust bunny?

      no

8.31.24  3:40 pm   I know u wrote a song abt it already but im stupid and need more clarification: what is love

      i don't know how to describe love, but "what is love" is a popular phrase. i assume here you are referring to the phrase and not the love. that's just my vague assumption in this case

8.31.24  2:48 pm   My boyfriend and I don't have a set in stone anniversary date, could you give us some random date we could celebrate instead? 

      january 1

8.31.24  2:38 pm   How do i know if a song is finished? 

      all songs are finished

8.31.24  2:37 pm   Am I sad?

      possibly sometimes

8.31.24  2:06 pm   your drums are so simple and complex at the same time

      most things are

8.31.24  1:46 pm   how much pancakes can people eat before they explode

      some people could explode from half a pancake. it really varies. this is not really my field of expertise

8.31.24  1:26 pm   why were you named after bill clinton 

      because george clinton was taken

8.31.24  11:56 am   do you believe in astrology 

      if you can describe what that is then maybe i could say whether i believe what you've described

8.31.24  11:41 am   Who was/is your biggest creative inspiration?

      creative inspiratin is so profound that it's completely impossible to compare it quantitatively with other creative inspirations

8.31.24  10:30 am   what is gerrymandering

      i think it's when you rearrange the boundary lines of your electoral districts to affect the results. a guy named gerry did this, and he made the district borders look like salamanders, to catch all the votes in just the right way

8.31.24  10:00 am   what do you think of school starting 

      it's a weird time because you don't know what to expect, and looking back at this moment will be strange later

8.31.24  7:55 am   what is the difference between rock and stone?

      the sound of the words

8.31.24  7:39 am   Are you feeling happy about yourself?

      sometimes

8.31.24  7:31 am   favourite song

      still haven't found one, so i'll have to make my own just in case

8.31.24  7:30 am   How do magnets work?

      maybe they think they're each other? no actually i'm not quite sure yet

8.31.24  3:54 am   how the hell are u in osu?

      they made me an offer i couldn't refuse. well i suppose i could have refused it, but for some reason i didn't

8.31.24  3:40 am   How do you throw a ball out of the window?

      maybe it could go out one window and directly into another window

8.31.24  3:25 am   Do you think about every word before you write them down into your lyrics, do they all have a reason and a purpose to be in your song or do you just go with the flow ?

      what i've found is if you try to unwrite the song, the song fights back and writes itself

8.31.24  2:37 am   Do you consider yourself a surrealist?

      surrealism is sort of like a mild connective agent that you only need from time to time. if you use it too much, it feels like cheating, but if you don't use it enough then that also feels like cheating

8.31.24  2:25 am   What is beautiful to you?

      it's impossible to predict

8.31.24  1:27 am   how is your day?

      pretty good

8.31.24  1:06 am   are you happy?

      sometimes

8.31.24  12:28 am   How did you find your way on a creative manner where you could just "fuck this im creating this" when you get personally mind blocked. I try to write song but then it looks just tame and boring and it feels like i dont have any creativity

      this is off the subject, but do you like to have fun

8.30.24  11:56 pm   How to make money fast 

      sell advice on how to make money fast. it's that simple. there's a lot of people who want to make money fast, so they'll buy it pretty fast

8.30.24  9:11 pm   do all the characters in your videos have names?

      no

      just one, but the problem is you need a lightbulb to install the onion first

8.30.24  8:10 pm   If life gave you lemons what would you do with them?

      i would give them back, to life

8.30.24  7:53 pm   What is stupidity? Is it a lack of intelligence, an unwillingness to learn, or something else?

      i don't really know. sometimes it means the other person doesn't get your logic. sometimes it means you don't get the other person's logic. in these types of cases, both people might call each other stupid

8.30.24  7:13 pm   Have you ever listened to Steely Dan? 

      yes i have. but, to be fair, i have also listened to things other than steely dan

8.30.24  7:11 pm   Thoughts on parades?

      they sometimes have trouble going around corners

Since then (2022-now) I've associated some of my personality with some of your ideas. I expect but do not encourage a one sentence answer expressing something and yet more than something

      that doesn't sound like 'from zero'. it sounds like you know quite a lot about what i'm doing

      no

      everything is a spirit. not sure what that would make me

      so crazy it just might work
